title: What Happened at Maryland State University
description: They Thought it was Just a Game.Four unlikely college students come together to conquer a supernatural entity known as the Dark Source on their college campus on All Hallows Eve night (Halloween) after their homecoming game with a state rival. Little do they know their families have been battling the Dark Source for hundreds of years. Will they be the group to finally defeat the force of the Source? Or is there something else at play?
author: Michelle Carey
